<h2>Protocol: Droplist</h2>
<p>Defines the interaction model for dropdown menus, including keyboard navigation, ARIA roles, and typeahead support.</p>
<h3>Features</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Keyboard navigation (Arrow keys, Home/End)</li>
  <li>Type-ahead (delegated to the <a href="/blocks/type-ahead/">Type-Ahead</a> block, not inlined)</li>
  <li>ARIA roles and properties</li>
</ul>
<p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-muted);">Type-ahead &mdash; typing characters to jump to a matching option &mdash; is provided by the standalone <a href="/blocks/type-ahead/">Type-Ahead</a> behavior so the same pattern is shared with listboxes, menus, and trees.</p>